# Mailing Lists

SPI offers a variety of mailing lists.  A description of each active list is below.   Most SPI mailing lists can be found [here](http://lists.spi-inc.org/listinfo/).

## Announce List

SPI makes official announcements on this list.  All SPI contributing [members](../membership/) are recommended to be on this [list](http://lists.spi-inc.org/listinfo/spi-announce/) or read it through the [archive](http://lists.spi-inc.org/pipermail/spi-announce/).

## Board List

The spi-board list is for SPI board members, legal counsel and associated project liaisons (who act in the capacity of board advisors).

## Private List

The spi-private list is open to all SPI contributing members.

## General List

The spi-general list is a public list for general discussion of Software in the Public Interest.

